  <body>
  
    <section name="Map reads with gmap step">

      <p>This step allow to map reads with the Gmap mapper program. 
      <b>Warning:</b> As gmap only handle FASTA input files, this step convert on the fly the FASTQ entries to FASTA. 
      This step is quite slow because an awk script is used to convert data.</p>  

      <ul>
    <li><b>Internal name</b>: gmap</li> 
        <li><b>Available</b>: Only in local mode</li>
        <li><b>Multithreaded in local mode</b>: Yes (mapper multithreading)</li>
        <li><b>Input</b>: filtered reads (e.g. <code>filtered_reads_1.fq</code>)</li>
        <li><b>Output</b>: alignments in SAM format (e.g. <code>mapper_results_1.sam</code>)</li>   
    <br/>
        <li><b>Optional parameters</b>:</li>
    <table>
                <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th><th>Default value</th></tr>
                <tr><td>mapperArguments</td><td>string</td><td>Mapper additional command line arguments</td><td></td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <br/>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </body>
  
